{"tid":1255799,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"保護後生，咪比他們做烈士","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:13:28.000Z","uid":267473,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"513624ed7ec91855db360b5d2ae431d07b3ab63a","tid":1255799,"uid":267473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:10:41.000Z","msg":"今日係銅記聽到幾個後生傾計，越講越激，話要學太古廣場那位烈士，係習總G20那天，幾個人一齊玩笨豬跳，迫政府撒！ 要習總及香港人知道林鄭黑警是滿手鮮血.... 聽到我心都離一離。<br />\n<br />\n這種行動過激了，要學鄺神說不流血，不被捕。<br />\n<br />\n其實帶口罩，帶保護裝備，推鉄欄阻擋，在黑警面前，這些只會給他們一個借口向你重擊，完全支撐不到5分鐘。<br />\n當你是手無寸鐵，和平的示威，他們可以用警棒嗎？他們可以用布袋彈和橡膠子彈嗎？<br />\n帶口罩和裝備只令對方有藉口動武，亦有機會假冒和滲透。<br />\n我想200萬和平遊行的市民，大部分都不是激進的。但和平並不代表他們軟弱。<br />\n不要讓這些人的心血白費"},{"pid":"f1f29ee34ca174e6c2dc2fa395248f285682d66c","tid":1255799,"uid":191453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU8fFf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU8fFf9.jpg&h=c6019c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKRASFu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKRASFu.png&h=eac30445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【警民大和解】警方高層不代表前線 市民應支持前線警員!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251511\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e569e560f6c51afbe1d06dcfe94a04718c1df0e0","tid":1255799,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}